lead_paragraph: Scott Schebler doubled with the bases loaded and one out in the ninth inning as the Cincinnati Reds took advantage of another meltdown by Philadelphia's bullpen and rallied to beat the Phillies 3-2 Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Schebler's Double in 9th Rallies Reds Over Phillies 3-2
